public interface StepType

Interface for classes that define how to run a step of a particular type. Implementing classes should be located in com.sebuilder.interpreter.steptype.

run

boolean run(TestRun ctx)
Perform the action this step consists of.

Parameters:
ctx - Current test run.
Returns:
Whether the step succeeded. This should be true except for failed verify steps, which should return false. Other failures should throw a RuntimeException.
